formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. The estimated costs mentioned in Column A is as provided by the management. The estimates should not be construed as certification of forecasts or estimates. The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances. 				
2. The details mentioned in Annexure A such as carpet area, booking status, unit consideration are as provided by the management. Received amount has been verified with the books of accounts. 				
3.The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing. 				
4. Land cost is considered as per Valuation report provided by Mr Hasmukh C Patel dated 05-02-21. Since land value as per current market value is considered, cost of land actually incurred and paid including stamp duty and registration fee of Rs 38,92,100 is not considered separately and included in acquisition cost of land mentioned. It should be noted that incurred and paid cost of land is Rs Rs 38,92,100 only.
5. The promoter has converted from Siddhi Developers to Siddhi Infralink Pvt Ltd and the same has been updated with RERA Authroity. The bank account is not updated yet till filing of this return. Books of accounts of Siddhi Developers as well as Siddhi Infralink Pvt Ltd have been relied upon for issuance of this certificate.
6. OD from Indian Bank has been sanctioned in the company by mortgage of security other than the project. As per mangagement, the same is not used for the project and hence cost is not considered.
